        <div class="doc-section" id="security">
            <h2>Security Protocols</h2>
            <h3>Access Controls</h3>
            <pre><code>
1. IP Location Verification
2. Time Window Restriction (9 AM - 5:30 PM)
3. Bcrypt Password Hashing
4. Session Encryption
5. Automatic Account Lockout
            </code></pre>

            <h3>Risk Mitigation</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>5 failed attempts ‚Üí Account block</li>
                <li>Admin approval required for new signups</li>
                <li>Automatic logout after 30min inactivity</li>
                <li>All security events logged in block.log</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

